  "notes": "Daughter of Farnan, slain by the Crimson Bat; scarred at Moonbroth. Natural born Ernaldori/Colymar leader, fearsome bison rider, and devout Orlanth Adventurous initiate. Uses Molon's +3D6 damage bonus for lance charges.",
